			Screensaver
			Configure screensaver settings
			by Tony Houghton

Brief
~~~~~
Screensaver lets you manage the X screensaver with ROX-Session.
New versions can be found here:

	http://rox.sourceforge.net

You need to be running a recent (0.1.25 or later) version of ROX-Session,
otherwise it won't work.


